schemas.name: schema.graphql
schemas.content:
schema {
  query: RootQueryType
  mutation: MutationRoot
}

"""food item"""
type food {
  """Resturent Object Id"""
  _id: ID

  """The id of the food item."""
  itemId: String

  """The name of the food."""
  foodName: String

  """The type of food. """
  foodType: String
}

"""food item"""
input foodinputitem {
  """The name of the food."""
  foodName: String

  """The type of food. """
  foodType: String
}

"""Mutation API"""
type MutationRoot {
  fooditemSave(inputItem: foodinputitem!): food
  resturentmenuItemSave(inputItem: resturentmutation!): resturent
}

"""resturent menu item"""
type resturent {
  """Resturent Object Id"""
  _id: ID

  """Resturent Item Id"""
  itemId: String

  """The name of the resturent."""
  resturentName: String

  """The type of menu a resturent have. """
  menuType: [String]
}

"""resturent menu items"""
input resturentmutation {
  """The name of the resturent."""
  resturentName: String

  """The type of menu a resturent have. """
  menuType: [String]
}

type RootQueryType {
  foodItem(itemId: ID!): [food]
  foodItems: [food]
  resturentCollection: [resturent]
}
